column5: there is a dog named patch that likes to steal fish at a camp i go to but not quite as bad a this  https://www.facebook.com/keithkavajecz/videos/540189466139440/
Too funny!  I've never messed with a mink before but I think I'd be letting him have a walleye rather than eat my fingers....
That's hilarious!!  I don't know what I would Do.  Likely arm myself with something..  My slush scoop has a built in ice chipper..
Worked at a mink farm for 2 weeks. Mean mean little ba#$%$$d.
Pretty persistent little guy.  Foods a little scarce that time of year so why not just let him have it?
That was hilarious.  I'm wondering how the mink found those guys way out on the ice, probably a remote location.
